query: WITH entities AS (SELECT customer_id, reference, id FROM deposits WHERE ((customer_id = $1) AND (COALESCE((reference, id) > ($4, $3), $3 IS NULL))) ORDER BY reference ASC, id ASC LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: DepositId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN deposit_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.reference asc, i.id asc, i.id, e.sequence
